---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Mission Trip to India — Go & Serve | Global Hope India"
  description="Join a short-term mission trip to India with Global Hope India. Over 1,000 Americans have traveled to empower the church, distribute Bibles, and transform lives."
  ogImage="https://assets.spiritmediapublishing.com/images/ghi-radical-group.jpg"
  keywords="short term mission trip India, mission trip to India, go to India missions, volunteer India Christian, serve the church in India"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script src="https://mail.spiritmediaone.com/js/form_embed.js" defer></script>
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "WebPage",
      "name": "Short Term Mission Trip to India",
      "description": "Join a short term mission trip to India. Over 1,000 Americans have traveled to India through Global Hope India to empower the church and advance the gospel.",
      "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Global Hope India", "url": "https://globalhopeindia.org" },
      "url": "https://globalhopeindia.org/give/mission-trips"
    })}></script>
  </Fragment>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[50vh] lg:min-h-[60vh] flex items-end overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#1D1C1C]" style="background-image:url('https://assets.spiritmediapublishing.com/images/ghi-radical-group.jpg');background-size:cover;background-position:center;"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 via-black/30 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 pb-12 pt-40">
      <p class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Mission Trips</p>
      <h1 style="color:white!important;" class="max-w-3xl font-bold text-[28px] md:text-[36px] lg:text-[50px] leading-[1.2]">Short Term Mission Trip<br/>to India</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/70 text-lg max-w-xl">God called every believer to go. Join over 1,000 Americans who have traveled to India to empower the church and advance the gospel.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IMPACT STATS -->
  <section class="bg-[#2EAB5A] py-10 px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center text-white">
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold">1,000+</p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mt-1">Americans sent to India</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold">139</p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mt-1">Mission teams deployed</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold">12</p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mt-1">Partner locations</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold">25+</p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mt-1">Years sending teams</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTENT -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[#1D1C1C] text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Why Go to India?</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-[#555] leading-relaxed">
            <p>Few experiences are more life-changing than a <strong>short term mission trip to India</strong>. When you step foot in India, you witness firsthand the spiritual hunger of 1.4 billion people — and you discover that God can use you to make an eternal difference.</p>
            <p>Our mission teams serve alongside <strong>12 indigenous church-planting partners</strong> located across North, South, East, and Northeast India. Teams participate in leadership development, child development, and community development — empowering the local church to make Christ known long after the team returns home.</p>
            <p>A mission trip to India through Global Hope India is more than a trip — it is a <strong>radical response to God's call</strong>. Over 1,000 Americans have been transformed by this experience, returning home with a deeper faith and a lifelong connection to God's work among India's unreached people.</p>

            <h3 class="text-[#1D1C1C] text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">3 Ways Teams Serve</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold">1.</span> <strong>Leadership Development</strong> — Equipping church planters, pastors, and worship leaders with biblical truth and practical resources.</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold">2.</span> <strong>Child Development</strong> — Serving children in schools, orphan homes, and local communities with education and the love of Christ.</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold">3.</span> <strong>Community Development</strong> — Clean water projects, hygiene kits, business development, and other practical resources that transform villages.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="bg-[#F8F5EF] rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h3 class="text-[#1D1C1C] text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-center">Ready to Go?</h3>
            <p class="text-[#555] text-sm mb-5 text-center">Fill out this form and our team will contact you with upcoming trip dates, costs, and details.</p>
            <form id="trip-form" class="space-y-3">
              <div>
                <label class="text-xs text-[#666] mb-1 block">Full Name *</label>
                <input type="text" name="name" required class="w-full border border-[#ccc] rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#2EAB5A] focus:border-transparent" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="text-xs text-[#666] mb-1 block">Email *</label>
                <input type="email" name="email" required class="w-full border border-[#ccc] rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#2EAB5A] focus:border-transparent" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="text-xs text-[#666] mb-1 block">Mobile</label>
                <input type="tel" name="mobile" class="w-full border border-[#ccc] rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#2EAB5A] focus:border-transparent" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="text-xs text-[#666] mb-1 block">When can you go? *</label>
                <input type="text" name="when" required class="w-full border border-[#ccc] rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#2EAB5A] focus:border-transparent" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="text-xs text-[#666] mb-1 block">Who will go with you?</label>
                <input type="text" name="who" class="w-full border border-[#ccc] rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#2EAB5A] focus:border-transparent" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="text-xs text-[#666] mb-1 block">Questions or specifics</label>
                <textarea name="specifics" rows="3" class="w-full border border-[#ccc] rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#2EAB5A] focus:border-transparent resize-none"></textarea>
              </div>
              <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-[#1D1C1C] text-white font-semibold text-sm rounded-lg py-2.5 hover:bg-[#333] transition-colors">Send My Interest</button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-[#2EAB5A] text-center py-12 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-white font-bold text-[26px] md:text-[36px] mb-4">Take the Next Step</h2>
      <p class="text-white/90 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">A short term mission trip to India will change your life — and the lives of those you serve. Join us and experience God's work among India's unreached people firsthand.</p>
      <a href="/get-involved" class="inline-block bg-white hover:bg-stone-100 text-[#2EAB5A] font-semibold text-lg px-10 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors shadow-md">Learn More About Getting Involved</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
